Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了她  杀了戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破魔之矢用光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
