Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀法变的这么迟钝
