Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个使用破魔之箭\N叫做戈薇的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有毒虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱来啊  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连毒蜂也吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你去追珊瑚还有戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  弥勒  你别死喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃吗
