Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也快点去追犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鬼竟然装出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连虫也舍不得杀的模样来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然还没\N从奈落手里解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是为了伤害戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺取四魂碎片而来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其让你继续受到奈落的利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁可…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  我马上就让你自由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你一个人走的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很快就会去陪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.34,0:15:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  快点去追珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你被琥珀弄伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮肉伤而已  而且那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他想杀我一定做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他却没那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚她不知道这些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也许打算把琥珀杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀没有一击让戈薇致命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么没有遵从奈落的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.79,0:16:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使被操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀还残留着人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.16,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得不太好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是姐弟呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  不要再离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我唯一的亲弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你之后我也会自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了把你从奈落手里夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你之后我也会自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了把你从奈落手里夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别阻止我  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀了琥珀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会让奈落称心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀  你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不给我醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同命令所说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫琥珀杀了戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀绝对不会违抗奈落的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想为什么琥珀会丧失记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是奈落操纵了他的心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说也对  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀自己也不愿想起往事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些不愿想起的记忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.29,0:19:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在琥珀面前不要再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人都想忘记的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.14,0:19:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落就让他忘得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要操纵琥珀纯洁的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对奈落而言是易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀!想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚和驱魔师的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都给我想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还想活下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能想起来并面对它的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的心就永远受奈落的控制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在体内的四魂碎片会被取走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被那家伙给杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得还真狠呢  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是想起自己做过什么的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子…真的会彻底崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他忘了一切的死去\N也是为了他好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  这下又…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下又回到起点了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.81,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是找麻烦的姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早告诉你不要那么冲动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确命令琥珀杀了戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是琥珀却没有杀了戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他还残存着人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不能杀琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.34,0:21:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要把他活生生的抢回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把你的性命延长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至让你忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然没有杀了戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在你还想取回人类的心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.82,0:22:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将一切都回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.62,0:22:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就对了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就暂时再让你活一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把一切都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  那个人的脸…无法消失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.89,0:23:49.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.04,0:24:01.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.28,0:24:08.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.36,0:24:17.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:24.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:31.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.15,0:24:38.89,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.62,0:24:46.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.03,0:24:54.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.16,0:25:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村子遭到盗贼的袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.93,0:25:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴虐无道的盗贼首领  蛾天丸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.07,0:25:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是化成人形的蛾妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.97,0:25:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉和弥勒法师一起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.91,0:25:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被困在毒茧当中了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.71,0:25:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同一时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.61,0:25:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找犬夜叉妖化之谜的杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.31,0:25:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然从老木妖怪那里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.68,0:25:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知一个恐怖的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.82,0:25:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的心被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.32,0:25:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
